  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-powered financial chat (Lab) with real-time streaming and rich component rendering",
    "Automated equity research PDF reports with charts, citations, and branded export",
    "SEC filing browser covering 40,000+ companies across 11+ global markets",
    "Document upload and analysis supporting PDF, CSV, XLSX, and images",
    "Custom Skills: reusable prompt templates for firm-specific workflows",
    "Organisation-level workspaces with role-based access control",
    "25+ live financial data sources including proprietary SEC pipeline",
    "Zero data retention — no cross-organisation data sharing",
    "Usage dashboard with activity analytics"
